# EDXcellence CRM â€” Full-Stack Role-Based Admin Panel  
A production-ready CRM system built with **React + Vite + Tailwind**, **NodeJS + Express**, and **MongoDB** featuring complete **Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)**.  
Designed for high-performance EdTech workflows: student lead management, deal tracking, user administration, analytics, and team operations.

